IETF WEBDAV Working Group Meeting

IETF-44, Minneapolis, Minnesota
March 17, 1999

A meeting of the WEBDAV Working Group was held March 17, 1999 in Minneapolis, Minnesota, as part of IETF-44. Prior to this meeting, an unofficial breakout sessions were held on the topic of advanced collections (March 16).
